"O: Really nice triple IPL. Huge hop flavors but bitterness is not off the charts. I like it like this, teeth-chattering bitterness can detract from the flavors sometimes. Don't get me wrong, it's very bitter and very dry but the hop flavors are the priority here. Lagering has made this one exceptionally smooth for a 10% triple IPL. No IPA of this caliber even comes close to the smoothness and drinkability."
